{"tid":1244712,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳芷尤返新加坡做女主角　片酬待遇倍增：唔考慮返TVB","createTime":"2019-06-20T04:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T03:39:48.000Z","uid":44730,"like":180,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"078f3a3f161fa7eeacf97fa65ea0a9698078aa93","tid":1244712,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2931674/org/d8ecf09db416e2fd77dbcaee03361737.jpg/xLqIxgjqq2PKeMCUPhDuMKK-8weoUcrkQ4JPgkOCT4I?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2931674%2Forg%2Fd8ecf09db416e2fd77dbcaee03361737.jpg%2FxLqIxgjqq2PKeMCUPhDuMKK-8weoUcrkQ4JPgkOCT4I%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=8cc7c5f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾在《城寨英雄》飾演四朵金花之一嘅陳芷尤（Apple），自從與張振朗分手後，隨即轉戰新加坡發展，並以國民電影《新兵正傳》打開知名度。本身喺新加坡長大嘅佢，講得一口流利英文，再加上打得又睇得，令陳芷尤拍畢《新》後，接連有電影以及網劇搵上門，過去一年多時間，陳芷尤將工作重心轉移到新加坡以及台灣，香港呢？只限探親。她接受《香港01》訪問時表示：「其實同TVB約都算完咗，雖然之後有傾過，但應該都唔會繼續。」"},{"pid":"d79eca3d87096f64eb8878626577b1e4768493e5","tid":1244712,"uid":49197,"like":55,"dislike":4,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:49:32.000Z","msg":"俾張振朗食過,不了"},{"pid":"0df127b4c8575058b4e00528566b682a3484c39c","tid":1244712,"uid":44730,"like":8,"dislike":36,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2931665/org/afef07f55367c89ce0527208ebe84d48.jpg/Dtot9WmOfbLO-uewvq7kFlvZor3bHzJ0Sh8g9kofIPY?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2931665%2Forg%2Fafef07f55367c89ce0527208ebe84d48.jpg%2FDtot9WmOfbLO-uewvq7kFlvZor3bHzJ0Sh8g9kofIPY%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=0c000b67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n30歲嘅陳芷尤於《我的左鄰右里》中扮演學生妹，佢笑言雖然唔係好突兀，但應該都係最後一次。"},{"pid":"09fe428fee32d1965bd6f14105f1b10751f28d24","tid":1244712,"uid":44730,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:50:07.000Z","msg":"之所以完全唔考慮TVB，除咗係因為未試過拍電影之外，喺新加坡嘅待遇亦甚為吸引。「價錢當然係好過TVB先會咁揀，同埋因為我喺香港藝人，所以又會再比多啲。」講完價錢，又不如講下工時，陳芷尤表示喺新加坡拍劇／戲，規定每日最多12小時、拍7日放1日，完全唔似得大台劇集，有開工無收工，所以整體來說都算輕鬆。「其實當初拍《新》時，最大擔心係因為呢個作品前幾集都有好好票房，我要加入時，好多人都會問點解搵香港藝人，自己係有壓力，好在出到嚟嘅反應都好好，年底會開第5集，我都會繼續參與。」"},{"pid":"64a68b409ac50f2fd86322d879133730a96851f9","tid":1244712,"uid":44730,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:51:08.000Z","msg":"由梁智強執導嘅《新》，係為紀念新加坡國民服役制度45周年而拍攝嘅作品，電影在當地上畫時，榮登新加坡影史上最賣座的華語片，亦因此帶來了續集嘅商機。陳芷尤當初透過朋友介紹下得到試鏡機會，她二話不說飛到新加坡與導演見面。「因為自己有睇開《新》，同埋未拍過電影，所以朋友話可以試鏡時，我諗都唔諗就飛咗去新加坡。」此外，她過去一年，亦先後與台灣女神安心亞合作電影《殺手不笨》、網劇《神奇之吻》、《我的左鄰右里》，就咁睇，都見到機會比大台多好幾倍，試問識得揀都都知道點揀啦。"},{"pid":"6425b5eef2ec6bfefd12023716d7f4cbd39b1b4e","tid":1244712,"uid":29070,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:52:14.000Z","msg":"張振朗條舊菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e37db83790b1268524961f22d4d5f727c3f339f","tid":1244712,"uid":60535,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:52:18.000Z","msg":"CCTVB其實都係踏腳石嚟啫，除咗啲老臣子，或者做戲屎撚到仆街頭垃圾要喺度R飯食之外，我諗唔到留喺度嘅理由"},{"pid":"d27a2ed3302a954c55f4ca6f2be13ccef2159b2e","tid":1244712,"uid":51041,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:52:37.000Z","msg":"樣靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />波大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8aa54bb19f3462bb7b68b7d636051efac1047ce","tid":1244712,"uid":44730,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2931748/org/fa3adef421d4a872a05919a2763ebfe9.jpg/Tpkup-VwXfFCY9CyRdETgLl6vWIdphemSfsDsUn7A7E?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2931748%2Forg%2Ffa3adef421d4a872a05919a2763ebfe9.jpg%2FTpkup-VwXfFCY9CyRdETgLl6vWIdphemSfsDsUn7A7E%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=3e5892a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳芷尤喺新加坡有屋企人同朋友，所以佢一啲都唔覺悶。"},{"pid":"11df6249b4b8d36c7d9e32a2da4a699e0c2c6ffa","tid":1244712,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:57:18.000Z","msg":"有！骨！氣！<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3306651467eafb84068ccbfa74c2499b135b253e","tid":1244712,"uid":77277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:59:00.000Z","msg":"原來佢同鷲哥係同鄉"},{"pid":"87fcf4808188883938c65a5babf55e91a49356d6","tid":1244712,"uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:11:04.000Z","msg":"小雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb39b646ab580c7fc93ff1ba3d9925cb0787064","tid":1244712,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:30:07.000Z","msg":"每日最多12小時<br />\n踩足的話都夠皮啦"},{"pid":"1cf6ee8f2505adaf7cf9be695e99f8ae4dafd6c8","tid":1244712,"uid":228223,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4e37db83790b1268524961f22d4d5f727c3f339f","tid":1244712,"uid":60535,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:52:18.000Z","msg":"CCTVB其實都係踏腳石嚟啫，除咗啲老臣子，或者做戲屎撚到仆街頭垃圾要喺度R飯食之外，我諗唔到留喺度嘅理由"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T07:15:22.000Z","msg":"花菇不遠萬里去Juilliard School讀夠四年，一畢業就有得同Nicole Hitman、Hugh Grant拍硬檔就係咁嘅原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de75634e324006aab54e36c24d13bee9069b10a5","tid":1244712,"uid":228223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d79